{"tid":2414516,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人口17年首跌 去年49,900淨移出創10年新高","createTime":"2021-02-19T12:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T12:54:42.000Z","uid":259010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a5582f5f7d15b28f55b1eb37be22b7c7e72a57","tid":2414516,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02ea2d83faa31b803a3192cdef4ca8bda5f460c","tid":2414516,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/CEH5LJPFPJDSLFGOC2UE6STHAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FCEH5LJPFPJDSLFGOC2UE6STHAU%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=fba3cf3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FCEH5LJPFPJDSLFGOC2UE6STHAU%2F&h=48ee772a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/CEH5LJPFPJDSLFGOC2UE6STHAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n樓跌喇"},{"pid":"85b6a57e79af87219e3b2a6bc9cc697728f4a5fb","tid":2414516,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=6505a874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】疫後一年，香港人口下降。政府統計處今日（18日）發表的數字顯示，2020年年底的本港人口的臨時數字約為747萬人，較前年年底的752萬人減少了4.65萬人，跌幅為0.6%。而去年有近5萬港人遷移出香港，創10年來新高！政府解釋，移出人口急升，與疫情下各地封關令往來人口減少，及不少離港居民繼續留在外地生活有關。至於去年持單程證移入本地的人口則僅10,100人，較前下跌74%。<br />\n<br />\n2020年年底的人口下跌由自然減少（即死亡多於出生）及香港居民淨移出（即移入少於移出）組成。2020年首次出現6,700人的自然減少，出生人數為43,100人，死亡人數為49,800人。同時，2020年的淨移出人數為39,800人，其中10,100人為單程證持有人的移入，49,900人為其他香港居民的淨移出。<br />\n<br />\n翻查統計處紀錄，2020年近5萬港人的净移出數字也自2010年以來的新高，統計處解釋，淨遷移涵蓋香港居民以工作和讀書等各種目的進出香港的流動，在概念上與移民並不相同。香港作為一個國際城市，人口的流動性一直很高。在2016年至2020年的5年間，除2018年外，不包括單程證持有人的香港居民均錄得淨移出。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，人口數字反映很大程度上由於在疫情下香港和世界其他地區實施關口管制和檢疫措施，以及國際行程所受到的嚴重影響，移入香港的人數（例如單程證持有人，外籍家庭傭工和透過各種入境計劃來港工作或讀書的人士）大幅下降。其中，在2020年抵港的單程證持有人數目較一年前下降了74%。同時，在疫情前已離港的"},{"pid":"53905644afabb7d795aa7d4805c7d8262ede4fa7","tid":2414516,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"股樓照升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24983e48bb439cb8b06b4793dd88fbb73002b3c9","tid":2414516,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"內地專才incoming<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383580c7734126981ccd99098d2c4c601ef2026e","tid":2414516,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"下年放十萬新港人填數"},{"pid":"82cd0ec93468d2398e498a3487b8458958ab1269","tid":2414516,"uid":60307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"大陸最多係咩，驚西咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8657a93e376ac334ca6aa8f2f6e2712bad6310","tid":2414516,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"股樓升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}